# Business Requirement Document (BRD)

---

# 1. Project Objective

Design and deploy a scalable healthcare membership ecosystem that enables:

- Patient acquisition through field teams
- Digital health card issuance
- Family health plan enrolment
- Hospital patient retrieval and service tracking
- Membership lifecycle management
- Billing and operational reporting
- WhatsApp / SMS / customer communications
- Multi-hospital operational expansion

---

