- Super Admin
- Operational Admin
- Field Executive
- Field Manager
- Hospital Reception
- Customer / Patient
- Finance Team
- Support Team

## Optional Future Roles

- Doctor
- Department Head
- Compliance Officer
- Analytics Manager
- Franchise / Partner Admin

## Role Purpose Summary

| Role | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| Super Admin | Full control over the platform |
| Operational Admin | Daily operations and oversight |
| Field Executive | Registers patients and distributes cards |
| Field Manager | Supervises field team performance |
| Hospital Reception | Retrieves patients and records visits |
| Customer / Patient | Views card, history, and notifications |
| Finance Team | Manages billing, revenue, and settlements |
| Support Team | Handles complaints and service queries |

